# Forms and User Interactions Guide

## Contact Form
### Endpoints
- Submit contact: `POST /api/forms/contact`
- Admin list: `GET /api/admin/contact-submissions`
- Admin update: `PUT/PATCH /api/admin/contact-submissions/{id}`
- Admin delete: `DELETE /api/admin/contact-submissions/{id}`

## Newsletter
### Endpoints
- Subscribe: `POST /api/newsletter/subscribe`
- Confirm: `POST /api/newsletter/confirm`
- Unsubscribe: `POST /api/newsletter/unsubscribe`
- Admin list: `GET /api/admin/newsletter-subscribers`
- Admin update: `PUT/PATCH /api/admin/newsletter-subscribers/{id}`
- Admin delete: `DELETE /api/admin/newsletter-subscribers/{id}`

## Event Registration
### Endpoints
- Register: `POST /api/events/{event_id}/register`
- Admin list: `GET /api/events/{event_id}/registrations`
- Admin update: `PUT/PATCH /api/admin/event-registrations/{id}`
- Admin delete: `DELETE /api/admin/event-registrations/{id}`

## Surveys
### Endpoints
- Get survey: `GET /api/surveys/{survey_slug_or_id}`
- Submit response: `POST /api/surveys/{survey_id}/responses`
- Admin results: `GET /api/admin/surveys/{survey_id}/results`

## Generic Forms
### Endpoints
- Submit form: `POST /api/forms/{form_identifier}/submit`
- Admin list: `GET /api/admin/form-submissions/{form_identifier}`
- Admin update: `PUT/PATCH /api/admin/form-submissions/{id}`
- Admin delete: `DELETE /api/admin/form-submissions/{id}`

